ending-on-himself\" id=\"_r_a_10493905408\" width=\"790\" height=\"1100\" alt=\"ChewMaN Worked at a tech start up right after this occurred. The company had just blew up and gotten a big investment and one employee decided he was gonna cash in on that. So he took the company credit card and whenever the company would be spending money on a client he would be spending it on himself.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e34\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10493906176/h695EAB21/any-clients-just-him-making-up-he-racked-almost-500k-debt-before-they-caught-on-and-firedsued-him\" id=\"_r_a_10493906176\" width=\"800\" height=\"652\" alt=\"Lavish trips to Vegas, 1000$ dinners, high end services. Only with him there wasn\u0026#39;t any clients it was just him making it up. He racked in almost 500k in debt before they caught on and fired/sued him.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e35\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10493905664/h08F65FCD/since-he-one-starting-employees-he-would-made-out-with-lot-cash-company-eventually-got-bought-out\" id=\"_r_a_10493905664\" width=\"770\" height=\"520\" alt=\"The sad thing since he was one of the starting employees he would of made out with a lot of cash when the company eventually got bought out.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAAL